| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1617 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 202807e8-8fe1-56ab-acc9-379d7be4e3b8"
